MEGA POST TODAY
I present the Mt Adams Stairs.

89 if you start up the right hand side at the beginning, or 90 if you start up the left. There's a park and overlook about midway.

Follow the long landing northeast alongside Columbia Parkway to 60 steps up to the pedestrian bridge.

At some point there was need to walk on the side of Rt 50 here, there are still 28 steps on the south side of Columbia Parkway. And 23 steps on the north side.

From the bridge there are 27 steps up to a landing on the side of the hill from which you can walk out to Oregon St or continue up 98 steps to the intersection of Celestial and Hill.

325 in total if you're looking for a bunch in one place just for the sake of the climb.

#yestergram #cincystairs #publicstairs #urbanexploring #activelifestyle #Cincinnati #cincinnatilandings #walkingthestepsofcincinnati #citystairs #publicstaircase #pedestrian #getoutside #socialdistancing #mtadams
